Name: Duck Force
About the game: Welcome to the Duck Force, recruit! Experience an amazing adventure in the rough stone age, where the bunny people under rule of a maniacal leader strives for the absolute power. Prove your skills in an epic air battle and show the crazy bunnies where a drake has his feathers! In varied levels, you must be stronger, faster and more skilled than your insidious opponents. Fly through dry deserts and rocky canyons full of challenges and evolve from a lame duck to a majestic flight artists. At the end of each climate zone a powerful boss is waiting for you. Will you be victorious at the end? By the Duck Force, we count on you!
